Example input data:
{
    "get": {
        # This maps data being returned by get
        "path/to/item": {
            "some_key": "content",
            "other_content": "content",
        },
        "other/path": {
            "other": "data",
        },
    },
    "ls": [
        "/path/item1",
        "/path/item2",
    ]
}

Build a SlackApiConfig object from a mapping object.

Input example:
    {
        'global': {
            'max_retries': 5,
            'timeout': 30
        },
        'methods': [
            {'name': 'users.list', 'args': "{"limit":1000}"},
            {'name': 'conversations.list', 'args': "{"limit":1000}"}
        ]
    }
